{"_path":"/maps/_science/complex-science","_dir":"_science","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"复杂科学","description":"复杂科学是一门研究复杂系统的学科，它涉及到多个学科领域，包括物理学、生物学、社会学、经济学等。复杂科学的研究对象是复杂系统，这些系统由大量相互作用的元素组成，这些元素之间的相互作用会导致系统的行为变得难以预测。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"components"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Components"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_science/systems-theory"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"系统论"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"阅读"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"阅读"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"老三论是复杂科学这个说法其实有失偏颇"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1i5411d7cn","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“老三论”是复杂科学？这个说法其实有失偏颇"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"老三论（系统论、控制论、信息论）试图用线性均衡理论去研究生物、通讯及社会问题，但非线性、非均衡的才是“复杂”。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"components","depth":2,"text":"Components"},{"id":"阅读","depth":2,"text":"阅读"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_science:complex-science.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_science/complex-science.md","_stem":"6.maps/_science/complex-science","_extension":"md"}